<p class="ql-align-center">有些孕妈担心</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">护肤品对胎儿有影响</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">所以干脆不用</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这也是不行的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但也没必要买什么「孕妇专用」</p>
